{{page-title "Help Ukraine"}}

<div class="intel-outer">
    <div>
        <div class="list-page-header">
            <h1>Help Ukraine</h1>
            <div>
                <img src="assets/images/help24.png" style="max-width: 600px;margin-top:20px"/>
            </div>
            <p>
                <a href="">United24</a> is the official site of the Ukrainian government collecting money for the war effort. 
                Consider donating.
            </p>

            <p>
                Why donate anywhere else? Smaller organization closer to the ground might be better at
                getting money where it needs to go without working its way through a large bureaucracy. 
            </p>

            <p>
                Also, consider other forms of help. We have experience tutoring online with ENGin which is cited below, and 
                can vouch its been a valuable experience for all involved. Please consider and if you've had good (or bad)
                experiences with other organizations, please <a href="mailto:uavictorycountdown@gmail.com">let us know</a>.
            </p>

        </div>
        {{#each this.model as |cat| }}
            <div class="intel-section">
                <div class='intel-section-title'>
                    <div class="intel-icon-div">
                          <span style="font-size: 0.9em; color: {{cat.iconcolor}};">
                            <FaIcon  class='intel-icon' @icon="{{cat.icon}}" />
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="intel">{{cat.name}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {{#each cat.subs as | sub | }}
                {{#if sub.name}}
                    <div class="subsection-title">
                        {{sub.name}}
                    </div>
                {{/if}}
                {{#each sub.links as |link| }}
                    <div class="intel-li">
                        <div class="intel-li-link">
                            <a href={{link.u}}>{{link.n}}</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="intel-li-desc">
                            {{{link.t}}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                {{/each}}
            {{/each}}
        {{/each}}
    </div>
</div>